            "title": "Veni grant: 'When duty calls: confronting fragmentation in crisis management'",
            "description": "The Veni grant programme is part of NWO\u2019s Talent Scheme. NWO seeks to provide opportunities for scientific creativity and unrestrained science. By encouraging innovative research, new lines of research arise that sometimes lead to surprising and even groundbreaking results. Therefore, NWO provides funds for curiosity driven research and talented scientists. Veni is aimed at excellent researchers who have recently obtained their doctorate. Researchers in the Talent Scheme are free to submit their own subject for funding. NWO selects researchers based on the quality of the researcher, the innovative character of the research, the expected scientific impact of the research proposal and the possibilities for knowledge use.",
